{"tid":2382006,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"隔牆有耳：請出獄手足 黃店受「嚴懲」（李八方）","createTime":"2021-01-27T04:08:48.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-31T12:31:07.000Z","uid":25558,"like":60,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"cf7793f426cc66a93f7bf5367047ecf19323f8d1","tid":2382006,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T04:08:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210127/2ZY2GF6HX5HXZBYBQOYGCZRMVY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210127%2F2ZY2GF6HX5HXZBYBQOYGCZRMVY%2F&d=vmCIlZEHEchodQF1AoZdn56X7PLg0GRX82CuX%2BG2FI0%3D&h=4f2b8488\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210127%2F2ZY2GF6HX5HXZBYBQOYGCZRMVY%2F&h=6e590ec0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210127/2ZY2GF6HX5HXZBYBQOYGCZRMVY/</a><br />\n<br />\n隔牆有耳：請出獄手足 黃店受「嚴懲」（李八方）<br />\n<br />\n香港人齊上齊落力撐手足同黃圈唔係得個講字，好似上年底逆巿開業嘅元朗黃店「亞萊泰菜」，想剛出獄手足可以過肥年，宣佈噚日請對方做「一日店員」，將全日營業額扣除成本全數出糧畀手足，結果大件事喇，開門前半個鐘已經排出人龍，到中午仲有近百人排隊等機會出手「懲罰」。<br />\n<br />\n「亞萊泰菜」老闆Oscar同八方講，因見到好多被捕同坐監手足有生活負擔，決定幫相識多時、出獄時銀行戶口得番300幾蚊嘅手足李先生，但對方堅拒接受捐款，於是改為請對方做一日店員，但冇諗過外界反應咁熱烈，同路人嘅「懲罰」真係唔係講笑，小店下晝一度出帖「求饒」，問可唔可以有中場休息「食枝煙」，但大家一於少理，仲有唔少留言話入緊去元朗幫襯，八方仲見元朗區議員張秀賢夜晚都有去，仲即場報料預計要等成個鐘，仲話「為咗支持手足都值嘅」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/mw9dGEloU1t9VUWQ6NdQhZALNqk=/1772x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/BDP6JDKZOJAF3KINWDKAX2M6PU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fmw9dGEloU1t9VUWQ6NdQhZALNqk%3D%2F1772x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FBDP6JDKZOJAF3KINWDKAX2M6PU.jpg&h=0a073de4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■老闆Oscar（左）同手足李先生都好有heart，同路人亦出力「懲罰」，齊心力量好感動呀！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一日店員：願捐人工予612<br />\n<br />\n做咗一日店員嘅李生坦言至今無悔，對唔少後生仔因為參與運動坐監感到心痛，佢亦冇打算袋起人工，因為知道612基金之前告急，希望將啲錢捐畀612，睇見香港人咁齊心，八方相信寒冬雖冷，但大家一齊逆風而行，一定可以走出黑暗。<br />\n<br />\n李八方<br />\n<br />\n===========<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n喊到鼻水都流埋<br />\n<br />\n香港人<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae7bb6f8ceddbec8829b1382a11db4fb70299037","tid":2382006,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T08:18:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2852fb6881646aad4c32a8f8a538bdf527d8844c","tid":2382006,"uid":53498,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T08:27:02.000Z","msg":"無人係condom<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c25518decd854257e6b6d81f1b72dd5647d4f3bf","tid":2382006,"uid":80393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T08:57:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc556fbbf51dfde37fcc83c2a760e7f0fc1af1ab","tid":2382006,"uid":353635,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T19:01:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7ba932c5f6e74cbdc245590a049c604b82a8b83","tid":2382006,"uid":25834